column2: Ford expands recall for vehicles with Takata airbagsFord CEO joins IBM board as auto industry transforms Jan 26 Ford Motor Co Chief Executive Mark Fields is joining IBM's board of directors as the No. 2 U.S. automaker explores alternative mobility options beyond selling cars and trucks.
